{"tid":1122221,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"香港戲院大發慈悲 今晚安排16場非《復仇者聯盟4》放映","createTime":"2019-04-23T23:02:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T02:44:56.000Z","uid":41453,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0cdb6b1a3b39968c6a17de09095c0071ce0b2b51","tid":1122221,"uid":41453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T23:02:56.000Z","msg":"迪士尼發行的《復仇者聯盟4終局之戰》將於明天正式上映，而該片未上映已先行打破多個紀錄。當中除了戲院提早開場紀錄、戲票票價上調幅度紀錄外，同時也令一眾上映中電影也需要作「終局之戰」。<br />\n<br />\n據初步估計，全港戲院明天共有約千三場的放映，不過當中《復仇者聯盟4終局之戰》卻已佔了1,159場，佔了全港上映場次88%，其餘十五部上映電影，卻要瓜分149場場次，當中晚上七時後的夜場，更只餘下16場。<br />\n<br />\n在十五部明天仍上映的電影裡，當中以高先發行、陳小娟執導的《淪落人》所佔場次最多，共有42場，其中八場為夜場，其次便是華納發行的《哭泣的女詭》，22場場次裡有三場夜場。其餘有夜場的電影，還包括了安樂發行的《三夫》與《冷血戰曲》、洲立發行的《孟買酒店》，以及高先發行的《天逆反擊戰：地球起義》，主要集中在百老匯電影中心與新光戲院Super 3三面幕影院。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/66729\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfilmblog.com%2Farchives%2F66729&d=zdm3SfM4sEUVnXmiquxubAoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=3a280c4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/66729</a>"},{"pid":"ecf738bb4944cdb284a037d318709a702d149670","tid":1122221,"uid":2035,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T23:04:58.000Z","msg":"16場咁多"},{"pid":"364bab958e74f81d7b260bb2cded062e4656092c","tid":1122221,"uid":34444,"like":3,"dislike":21,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T23:13:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea359303fd10765f205002d9e3d85c442bae74ca","tid":1122221,"uid":109780,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T23:40:04.000Z","msg":"樓上又copy我段文字劇透<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"87c76174c7a09df293b7a933355349ee500ee22a","tid":1122221,"uid":41453,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"ecf738bb4944cdb284a037d318709a702d149670","tid":1122221,"uid":2035,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T23:04:58.000Z","msg":"16場咁多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T23:44:37.000Z","msg":"企業社會責任"},{"pid":"fdfb66f9d4b8c342940a016b149a0d0f3a4e1f17","tid":1122221,"uid":41453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T02:42:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"106fb87426e6bcfa0067dba3511832491705b7e3","tid":1122221,"uid":32934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T02:44:56.000Z","msg":"非份熟女摺得未"}]}